{
  "stem": "8252.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Oh, probably tomorrow morning, because they don't work at night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They work 9 to 5.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's what they believed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Look, there was some-- some reason to that belief.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because at that time, the bazookas were in the hands of children, German children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were lying at the roads in ditches with bazookas and hitting the American tanks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So the American tanks didn't advance too much in the night because of that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But anyhow, hearing that and knowing that my guards decided that they will move across the river, I decided that I'm not going to stay with them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went into a barn, and dig a hole in a pile of hay, and hid there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I hid there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I broke away from them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't cross, and they were still there the next day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the next morning, very early in the morning, I hear a big noise on the road in front of that farm, and I come out.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you have to know that by that time, I didn't have a uniform of any nation.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was in a combination of all the uniforms.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And first time I hear, stop, who's there?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's an American who doesn't know what he's seeing, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, I am friend, friend.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't know too much English yet at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then the Americans start jumping out of the tank.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the first one said he's Swedish, the other is Ukrainian, the third one is Irish, and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I say, where are the Americans?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Oh, we are all Americans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was my first encounter with the melting pot of United States.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I found out right away that the guards were still there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took care of the guards, the American soldiers.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
